code: public static boolean isEmpty(int[] array) {     return (array == null || array.length == 0). }
public static boolean isEmpty(byte[] array) {     return (array == null || array.length == 0). }
public static boolean isEmpty(Object[] array) {     return (array == null || array.length == 0). }
public static <K, E extends Enum<E>> Map<K, E> mapEnum(Class<E> clazz, Function<E, K> mapper) {     return Arrays.stream(clazz.getEnumConstants()).collect(toMap(mapper, Function.identity())). }
